.TH wxHtmlLinkEvent 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxHtmlLinkEvent \- This event class is used for the events generated by \fIwxHtmlWindow\fR.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
This class is derived, and can use functions, from:


.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}.PP
\fIwxCommandEvent\fR

.RE


.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}.PP
\fIwxEvent\fR

.RE

.PP
wxWidgets docs: wxHtmlLinkEvent

.SS "Events"

.PP
Use \fIwxEvtHandler:connect/3\fR with \fIwxHtmlLinkEventType\fR to subscribe to events of this type.

.SH DATA TYPES
.LP
.B
\fBwxHtmlLink() :: #wxHtmlLink{}.\fR

.br
.RS

.RE
.B
\fBwxHtmlLinkEvent() :: wx:wx_object().\fR

.br
.RS

.RE
.B
\fBwxHtmlLinkEventType() ::\fR
\fB          command_html_link_clicked | html_cell_clicked |\fR
\fB          html_cell_hover.\fR

.br
.RS

.RE
.SH FUNCTIONS
.LP
.B
\fBgetLinkInfo(This) -> wx:wx_wxHtmlLinkInfo()\fR
\fB                     when This :: wxHtmlLinkEvent().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Returns the \fIwx_wxHtmlLinkInfo()\fR which contains info about the cell clicked and the hyperlink it contains.


.RE
